title: Kamome no Koto wa Yoku Shiranai
original_name: かもめのことはよく知らない
sinopse:
A collection of loosely connected one-shots revolving around the residents of a small island town. Little snippets of life, love, and growth.

1. Nana Kairi no Hanashi
2. Kamome no Koto wa Yoku Shiranai
3. Yoru no Tobari
4. Hakka
5. Mushikui Machi nite
6. Caramel-kun
7. Sumire
8. Tsugumi no Koto
